ed artists}}\n[[Category:21st century-related lists]]\n[[Category:Music-related lists]]\n[[Category:Lists of Internet-related superlatives]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n[[The Weeknd]] has the most monthly listeners on Spotify as of April 2020.]]\nThis list contains the most-streamed artists on the [[Streaming media|audio streaming]] platform [[Spotify]]. As of April 2020, [[The Weeknd]] has the most monthly listeners on Spotify, and [[Ed Sheeran]] has the most [[Friending and following|followers]]. Since 2013, Spotify has published a yearly list of its most-streamed artists, which has been topped by [[Drake (musician)|Drake]] a record three times during the years (2015, 2016, and 2018).\n\n==Most monthly listeners==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Rank\n!Artist\n! Listeners per month<br />(millions)\n! Class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Chg|Change (weekly)}}\n! class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! 1\n|[[The Weeknd ]] || align=\"center\" | 62.12|| align=\"center\" |{{Increase}}|| align=\"center\" |<ref name=\"The Weeknd\" />{{fv|date=March 2020|reason=Provided link goes to the artist's page on Spotify, and doesn't substantiate the ranking given here.}}\n|-\n! 2\n|[[Justin Bieber]]|| align=\"center\" | 61.80|| align=\"center\" |{{Decrease}}|| align=\"center\" |<ref name=\"Justin Bieber\" />{{fv|date=March 2020|reason=Provided link goes to the artist's page on Spotify, and doesn't substantiate the ranking given here.}}\n|-\n! 3\n|[[Ed Sheeran]]|| align=\"center\" | 56.92|| align=\"center\" |{{Decrease}}|| align=\"center\" |<ref name=\"Ed Sheeran\" />{{fv|date=March 2020|reason=Provided link goes to the artist's page on Spotify, and doesn't substantiate the ranking given here.}}\n|-\n! 4\n|[[Dua Lipa]]|| align=\"center\" | 56.20|| align=\"center\" |{{Increase}}|| align=\"center\" |<ref name=\"Dua Lipa\">{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/6M2wZ9GZgrQXHCFfjv46we|title=Dua Lipa|website=Spotify|accessdate=Marc